              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/43039612/" class="">法国：埃菲尔铁塔披上中国红</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/stupybighead/" class=" " title="stupybighead">stupybighead</a>
              
